### Create employee
POST http://localhost:8081/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "position": "Backend Developer"
}

### List employees (optional filters)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees?department=Engineering&position=Backend%20Developer

### Get employee by id
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/1

### Update employee department/position
PUT http://localhost:8080/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "department": "Platform",
  "position": "Tech Lead"
}

### Delete employee
DELETE http://localhost:8080/employees/1
